abstract: Editorial holds Libyans need to get beyond the horrors and focus on creating a free and productive country; warns if not, they risk even more chaos and suffering; urges United States and Europe to help and goad Libyans into building a peaceful democracy.
snippet: Libyans must resist reprisals and channel their passion into building a free and productive country. If not, they risk even more chaos and suffering.
